            {
              "content": "=You are a support ticket classifier. Classify the following support request into exactly one of these three categories: billing, technical, general.\n\nRespond with only the category word in lowercase. Nothing else. No punctuation, no explanation.\n\nSupport request:\n{{ $json['Describe your issue'] }}"
