    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## What this Workflow does\n- A user fills out a support form. An LLM reads the issue description and classifies it into one of three categories: billing, technical, or general. The workflow automatically routes the ticket to the correct branch, notifies the team on Slack via a sub-workflow, and returns a confirmation message to the user. No manual trigger needed.",
        "height": 176,
        "width": 496
      },
