    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Code node\nCleans and validates the LLM output - strips whitespace, lowercases, removes punctuation. Defaults to \"general\" if the LLM returns something unexpected. Also explicitly pulls the form fields forward so all downstream nodes have access to them.",
